    key_facts: ['Communities are made up of individuals, families, businesses, schools, and organizations.', 'Local leaders — like principals, pastors, and business owners — shape community culture.', 'Everyone in a community has both rights and responsibilities.', 'Strong communities are built on trust, communication, and shared values.'],
